===佛教===
[[佛教|佛教]]现在被认为是西方世界里信众发展最快的主要宗教之一，而除此以外，西方人研究佛学的人数也大为增加（即使他们不是信徒）。<ref>[http://www.asiantribune.com/?q=node/10418 {{Wayback|url=http://www.asiantribune.com/?q=node%2F10418 |date=20171102201751 }} Buddhism fastest growing religion in West | Asian Tribune<!-- Bot generated title --></ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.amazon.co.uk/Western-Buddhism-insights-religion-Insights/dp/0722532326 |title=Western Buddhism: New insights into the West fastest growing religion: New Insights into the Wests Fastest Growing Religion: Amazon.co.uk: Kulananda: Books<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2013-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927062452/http://www.amazon.co.uk/Western-Buddhism-insights-religion-Insights/dp/0722532326 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

佛教是美国和西欧国家发展最快的宗教之一。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.religionnewsblog.com/1079/buddhism-in-france-is-booming |title=Buddhism in France is booming buddhism-in-france-is-booming Buddhism in France is booming |accessdate=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2016-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110234959/http://www.religionnewsblog.com/1079/buddhism-in-france-is-booming |dead-url=no }}</ref>在澳大利亚，信仰佛教的人数从1996年的20万人增加到2001年的35.8万人，增速达到79.1%。<ref>[http://www.abs.gov.au/Ausstats/abs@.nsf/0/9658217eba753c2cca256cae00053fa3?OpenDocument Year Book Australia, 2003] {{Wayback|url=http://www.abs.gov.au/Ausstats/abs@.nsf/0/9658217eba753c2cca256cae00053fa3?OpenDocument |date=20170827043733 }} Australian Bureau of Statistics</ref>佛教甚至在英格兰的监狱中也传了开来，其信众人数十年内增长8倍。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/religion/5977093/Buddhism-is-fastest-growing-religion-in-English-jails-over-past-decade.html | location=London | work=The Daily Telegraph | first=Martin | last=Beckford | title=Buddhism is fastest-growing religion in English jails over past decade | date=2009-08-05 | accessdate=2013-07-21 | archive-date=2010-03-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100318064119/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/religion/5977093/Buddhism-is-fastest-growing-religion-in-English-jails-over-past-decade.html | dead-url=yes }}</ref>佛教在中国早就是传统宗教，在澳门，佛教也是澳门现今发展速度最快的宗教之一。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://history.cultural-china.com/en/43History6784.html |title=Religion in Macau |accessdate=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2012-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104023303/http://history.cultural-china.com/en/43History6784.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===基督教===
[[File:Zhangjiang_church,shanghai,china.jpg|thumb]]
[[基督教|基督教]]在非西方国家（东亚、非洲等地）发展势头迅猛。其中[[五旬节运动|五旬节运动]]是推广基督教的一个重要推动力。<ref name="Barker">{{cite web |year= 2005 |last= Barker |first= Isabelle V. |pages= 2, 8 and footnote 14 on page 8 |url= http://www.allacademic.com//meta/p_mla_apa_research_citation/0/3/9/8/7/pages39879/p39879-1.php |title= Engendering Charismatic Economies: Pentecostalism, Global Political Economy, and the Crisis of Social Reproduction |publisher= American Political Science Association |accessdate= March 25, 2010 |archive-date= 2013-12-17 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131217004703/http://citation.allacademic.com/meta/p_mla_apa_research_citation/0/3/9/8/7/pages39879/p39879-1.php |dead-url= no }}</ref>

在越南，基督教信众在1995年至2005年增长了600%。<ref name="liberty">{{cite web |author= |title=Annual Report on International Religious Freedom for 2005 - Vietnam |work=U.S. Department of State |date=2005-06-30 |url=http://www.unhcr.org/cgi-bin/texis/vtx/rsd/rsddocview.html?tbl=RSDCOI&id=437c9cdd2&count=0 |accessdate=2007-03-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061020211314/http://www.unhcr.org/cgi-bin/texis/vtx/rsd/rsddocview.html?tbl=RSDCOI&id=437c9cdd2&count=0 |archivedate=2006-10-20 }}</ref>在尼日利亚，基督徒的人数在2003年已经占到全国人口比重48.2%，比1953年的21.4%大幅增长。在南非，参加[[五旬节运动|五旬节运动]]的人在2001年已经达到总人口的7.1%（1951年只有0.2%）。一项2005年的统计显示，在韩国，基督教信仰者占总人口的29.2%，比1985年的20.7%大幅上涨。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pewforum.org/world-affairs/countries/?countryID=150 |title=Religious Demographic Profiles - Pew Forum |accessdate=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2010-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100421200729/http://pewforum.org/world-affairs/countries/?countryID=150 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pewforum.org/Politics-and-Elections/Presidential-Election-in-South-Korea-Highlights-Influence-of-Christian-Community.aspx |title=Pew Forum - Presidential Election in South Korea Highlights Influence of Christian Community |accessdate=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2013-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130310001353/http://www.pewforum.org/Politics-and-Elections/Presidential-Election-in-South-Korea-Highlights-Influence-of-Christian-Community.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref> 
然而，由于教会丑闻等负面因素，韩国的基督新教发展趋势放缓，已经被天主教和佛教取代。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://reconcilers.wordpress.com/2012/04/26/new-realities-facing-korean-christianity |title=new-realities-facing-korean-christianity |accessdate=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2013-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002233151/http://reconcilers.wordpress.com/2012/04/26/new-realities-facing-korean-christianity/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在中国，基督教信众的大幅增长甚至被称为“基督教史上最伟大的复兴”。尽管在二十世纪后期基督教在中国大陆长期遭受打压或限制，基督徒的人口仍然发展到了中国人口的百分之五。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://standpointmag.co.uk/april-13-features-the-middle-kingdoms-problem-with-religion-simon-scott-plummer-christianity-china |title=The Middle Kingdom's Problem with Religion |accessdate=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2013-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130819153535/http://standpointmag.co.uk/april-13-features-the-middle-kingdoms-problem-with-religion-simon-scott-plummer-christianity-china |dead-url=no }}</ref>一些乐观的媒体甚至估计，当今中国皈依基督教的人口每天达到三万人。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.charismamag.com/spirit/revival/14745-the-biggest-revival-in-history | title=The Biggest Revival in History | publisher=Chrisma Magazine | date=2012-11-15 | accessdate=2013-07-21 | archive-date=2013-08-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130810102058/http://www.charismamag.com/spirit/revival/14745-the-biggest-revival-in-history | dead-url=no }}</ref>在未来的一段时间里，预计中国的基督教发展趋势仍然保持迅猛，在2040年甚至可以从现在的数千万人发展到4亿人，使得中国成为世界上基督教人口最多的国家。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/belief/2010/aug/28/china-future-christianity |title=China: the future of Christianity? {{!}} Antonio Weiss {{!}} Comment is free {{!}} guardian.co.uk<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2012-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121218213840/http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/belief/2010/aug/28/china-future-christianity |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-14838749 |title=Christians in China: Is the country in spiritual crisis? |accessdate=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2017-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171231162154/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-14838749 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

基督教也在一些传统的天主教国家快速传播。例如天主教传统的巴西，基督新教的信仰人口比例在2010年已达到22.2%，使得传统天主教的信仰人口比例首次跌破70%。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/765590452/Millions-of-Brazilians-march-for-Jesus.html |title=Millions of Brazilians march for Jesus {{!}} Deseret News<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2013-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927115012/http://www.deseretnews.com/article/765590452/Millions-of-Brazilians-march-for-Jesus.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.getreligion.org/2012/07/french-evangelicals-through-an-american-lens/ |title=French Evangelicals through an American lens<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-07-21 |archive-date=2014-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141224115336/http://www.getreligion.org/2012/07/french-evangelicals-through-an-american-lens/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{pt}} [http://delas.ig.com.br/comportamento/numero+de+brasileiros+catolicos+cai+abaixo+dos+70+pela+1+vez/n1597173666158.html Percent of Brazilian Catholics is below 70% for the first time] {{Wayback|url=http://delas.ig.com.br/comportamento/numero+de+brasileiros+catolicos+cai+abaixo+dos+70+pela+1+vez/n1597173666158.html |date=20180825115340 }}</ref>

====摩门教====
1830年代创立的[[摩门教|摩门教]]的信仰人口数在过去数十年来也大幅增长。摩门教的信仰人口在1830-1850年代平均每年增长10%到25%，1850年后每年约增长4%。20世纪初期每年增长2%，1960年代增快到6%，1990年代降到4%到5%。而1990年后直到21世纪，其人口年增速又进一步放慢到每年2.5%，但仍比世界人口增长率（1.2%）高出一倍。预计如果摩门教的人口以每十年30%到50%的速度增长，其世界地位将在21世纪末显著提高，成为主流宗教。<ref>[http://www.bandung2.co.uk/books/files/religion/the%20rise%20of%20mormonism.pdf] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bandung2.co.uk/books/files/religion/the%20rise%20of%20mormonism.pdf |date=20130309030322 }} The Rise of Mormonism</ref>在美国，摩门教的人口以每年1.6%的速度增长，大约同等于美国的人口增速，成为基督教人口增速最快的教派之一（许多教派甚至负增长）。<ref>{{citation|url = http://commons.trincoll.edu/aris/files/2011/12/Mormons2008.pdf|title = Mormons in the United States 1990-2008: Socio-demographic Trends and Regional Differences|first1 = Rick|last1 = Phillips|first2 = Ryan T.|last2 = Cragun|publisher = Trinity College|accessdate = 2013-07-21|archive-date = 2013-07-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130708174548/http://commons.trincoll.edu/aris/files/2011/12/Mormons2008.pdf|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{citation|first = Joanna|last = Brooks|authorlink = |date = February 2, 2012|title = Mormon Numbers Not Adding Up|publisher = Religion Dispatches|url = http://www.religiondispatches.org/archive/culture/5611/mormon_numbers_not_adding_up/|accessdate = 2013-07-21|archive-date = 2014-06-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140603201621/http://www.religiondispatches.org/archive/culture/5611/mormon_numbers_not_adding_up|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.usatoday.com/news/religion/2011-02-16-church_growth_15_ST_N.htm |title= Growth stalls, falls for largest U.S. churches |first= Richard |last= Yeakley |date= February 15, 2011 |newspaper= [[USA_Today|USA Today]] |agency= (Religion News Service) |accessdate= 2013-07-21 |archive-date= 2012-07-12 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120712104601/http://www.usatoday.com/news/religion/2011-02-16-church_growth_15_ST_N.htm |dead-url= no }}</ref>

